# Binary Options Trading Bot Configuration
# 
# STEP 1: Get your API token from Deriv
# 1. Go to: https://app.deriv.com/account/api-token
# 2. Login to your account (create one if needed)
# 3. Click "Create new token"
# 4. Name it "Trading Bot" 
# 5. Enable "Trading" permissions
# 6. Copy the generated token below
#
# STEP 2: Choose account type
# - For DEMO trading: Use a demo account token (recommended for testing)
# - For REAL trading: Use a real account token (only after successful testing)

# Deriv API Credentials
DERIV_APP_ID=1089
DERIV_TOKEN=your_actual_token_here

# IMPORTANT: Replace 'your_token_here' with your actual token from Deriv
# Example demo token format: demo_abc123def456ghi789
# Example real token format: abc123def456ghi789